   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="letter">
            <pb n="1" facs="Edgeworth_NLS_23131_XXXX-08-14_page01.jpg"/><note>12</note>
            <opener>
               <salute>My dear <persName ref="./Personography.xml#EdgeM1">Miss Edgeworth</persName></salute></opener><p>You will be shocked to hear<lb/>
                  that we have this day lost <persName ref="./Personography.xml#ScotA1">Anne Scott</persName><lb/>
                  carried off in 14 days by brain fever in<lb/>
                  the prime of her life - apparently but<lb/>
                  yesterday in high health. The calamities<lb/>
                  of latter years had been too much for her<lb/>
                  nerves.<lb/>
                  <persName ref="./Personography.xml#LockS1">Sophia</persName> in her distress reminds me to send<lb/>
                  you this line ever</p><closer>yours very Sincerely<lb/>
               <persName ref="./Personography.xml#LockJ1">J<unclear></unclear> Lockhart<lb/></persName><lb/>
               <dateline>
                  <placeName ref="./Placeography.xml#London_ENK">London</placeName><date when="1833-06-25">June 25<hi rend= "superscript">th</hi>1833</date></dateline></closer> 
         </div>
